<td style="width: 50%;">
<p>Anne Devries, Library Technician<br />Tel: 905-522-1155 ext. 36322<br />Fax: 905-575-6035<br />Email:&nbsp;<a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="mailto:adevries@stjoes.ca">adevries@stjoes.ca</a></p>
